nodes.text: An Ottegan was a senator of the New Republic's Galactic Senate in 5 ABY. During Liberation Day, a day of celebration held on the planet Chandrila to mark the liberation of rebel prisoners from Ashmead's Lock on Kashyyyk, the senator was in a hall of the Old Gather-House, a historic building in Hanna City the capital city of Chandrila, where they were killed. Former New Republic pilot Norra Wexley spotted the senator as she made her way through the building after the former prisoners, who were secretly under the influence of inhibitor chips, attempted to assassinate New Republic leaders and noted that the senator's eyes were as glassy and as dead as a droids.
